&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align="center"&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.geocachealaska.org" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;img src="http://www.geocachealaska.org/images/GAKwolf1.jpg" alt="www.geocachealaska.org" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

</groundspeak:long_description><groundspeak:encoded_hints>On the ground</groundspeak:encoded_hints><groundspeak:logs><groundspeak:log id="946871725"><groundspeak:date>2020-07-20T12:26:42</groundspeak:date><groundspeak:type>Write note</groundspeak:type><groundspeak:finder id="7419128">Profbrad</groundspeak:finder><groundspeak:text encoded="false">This one was archived shortly before my visit, but I had it on my list still so I stopped to enjoy a great trip around the lake - proving once again that you don’t need a cache to make a visit worth it. Still, I would have loved to have signed something here. Lol!</groundspeak:text></groundspeak:log><groundspeak:log id="940792305"><groundspeak:date>2020-06-30T12:00:00</groundspeak:date><groundspeak:type>Unknown</groundspeak:type><groundspeak:finder id="410459">AKStafford</groundspeak:finder><groundspeak:text encoded="false">This cache will be officially archived. The new Cache Across America - Alaska is https://coord.info/GC8VWY0
I loved the Reflections Lake location and it's still worth a visit. But the cache being here took too much muggle activity.</groundspeak:text></groundspeak:log><groundspeak:log id="940792477"><groundspeak:date>2020-06-30T08:03:14</groundspeak:date><groundspeak:type>Archived</groundspeak:type><groundspeak:finder id="410459">AKStafford</groundspeak:finder><groundspeak:text encoded="false">The new Cache Across America - Alaska cache is located here: https://coord.info/GC8VWY0</groundspeak:text></groundspeak:log><groundspeak:log id="940687068"><groundspeak:date>2020-06-29T12:00:00</groundspeak:date><groundspeak:type>Unknown</groundspeak:type><groundspeak:finder id="410459">AKStafford</groundspeak:finder><groundspeak:text encoded="false">A replacement CAA cache has been hidden in a completely new location about 10 miles away. I am awaiting Reviewer approval and listing of the new cache and then this cache will be archived.</groundspeak:text></groundspeak:log><groundspeak:log id="928582186"><groundspeak:date>2020-05-19T12:00:02</groundspeak:date><groundspeak:type>Unknown</groundspeak:type><groundspeak:finder id="410459">AKStafford</groundspeak:finder><groundspeak:text encoded="false">This area has gotten more and more popular and the muggle action on this cache is more than I can manage. 
Disabling for now while I rework the hide. If you were coming to Alaska for the CAA series, contact me and we’ll work out the details for you to claim a find. 
Hoping to get a new hide up within a few days. </groundspeak:text></groundspeak:log></groundspeak:logs></groundspeak:cache></wpt><wpt lat="61.560083" lon="-149.480333"><time>2006-10-12T00:00:00</time><name>GCYV5X</name><desc>Cache Across America – Alaska by AKStafford</desc><url>https://www.geocaching.com/geocache/GCYV5X</url><urlname>Cache Across America – Alaska</urlname><sym>Geocache</sym><type>Geocache|Traditional Cache</type><groundspeak:cache id="477988" available="false" archived="true"><groundspeak:name>Cache Across America – Alaska</groundspeak:name><groundspeak:placed_by>AKStafford</groundspeak:placed_by><groundspeak:owner id="410459">AKStafford</groundspeak:owner><groundspeak:type>Traditional Cache</groundspeak:type><groundspeak:container>Small</groundspeak:container><groundspeak:attributes><groundspeak:attribute id="6" inc="1">Recommended for kids</groundspeak:attribute><groundspeak:attribute id="1" inc="1">Dogs</groundspeak:attribute><groundspeak:attribute id="13" inc="1">Available 24/7</groundspeak:attribute><groundspeak:attribute id="7" inc="1">Takes less than one hour</groundspeak:attribute><groundspeak:attribute id="25" inc="1">Parking nearby</groundspeak:attribute><groundspeak:attribute id="32" inc="1">Bicycles</groundspeak:attribute><groundspeak:attribute id="40" inc="1">Stealth required</groundspeak:attribute><groundspeak:attribute id="33" inc="1">Motorcycles</groundspeak:attribute><groundspeak:attribute id="15" inc="1">Available in winter</groundspeak:attribute></groundspeak:attributes><groundspeak:difficulty>1</groundspeak:difficulty><groundspeak:terrain>1.5</groundspeak:terrain><groundspeak:country>United States</groundspeak:country><groundspeak:state>Alaska</groundspeak:state><groundspeak:short_description>&lt;p align="center"&gt;&lt;a rel="nofollow" href=
