&lt;p align="left"&gt;Largest City: Jackson&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align="left"&gt;Size Rank: 32nd&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align="left"&gt;Population Rank: 31st&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align="left"&gt;Admission to Union: 20th&lt;/p&gt;
