&lt;td height="61" bgcolor="#FFFFFF"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About this cache:&lt;/strong&gt; Nashville is known for many
things, including its universities and colleges, top-notch medical
facilities and of course MUSIC! This cache is located near a spot
that affords a beautiful view of the rolling hills of Middle
Tennessee and the Nashville skyline. You may have to drive a short
distance down the hill to get the best views during the
summer.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td height="61" bgcolor="#CCCCCC"&gt;
