ark ~ 0.15 mile away</desc><url>https://www.geocaching.com/seek/wpt.aspx?WID=19a6123c-b6b0-4f46-be25-1d96c22b5b18</url><urlname>Park ~ 0.15 mile away</urlname><sym>Parking Area</sym><type>Waypoint|Parking Area</type></wpt><wpt lat="42.955" lon="-78.91"><time>2006-08-06T13:01:56</time><name>PKXJ03</name><cmt>Park here at the ice rink and cross over the highway on the pedestrian bridge.</cmt><desc>Parking</desc><url>https://www.geocaching.com/seek/wpt.aspx?WID=514f8dbb-9473-4fac-a633-41ec883e3989</url><urlname>Parking</urlname><sym>Parking Area</sym><type>Waypoint|Parking Area</type></wpt><wpt lat="36.503917" lon="-79.769167"><time>2009-02-20T07:32:19</time><name>EWXFVV</name><cmt>Use this WiFi hotspot to log caches or search for new ones. It's my personal network and is free to all cachers, no strings attached.  call me for password.  336-589-6664</cmt><desc>erikwillke's free WiFi hotspot</desc><url>https://www.geocaching.com/seek/wpt.aspx?WID=6f50717b-9dde-45e7-bbe3-0b54b117d5c5</url><urlname>erikwillke's free WiFi hotspot</urlname><sym>Reference Point</sym><type>Waypoint|Reference Point</type></wpt><wpt lat="41.958666666666666" lon="-75.65916666666666"><time>2006-09-07T18:06:12</time><name>PKY6HQ</name><cmt /><desc>Parking</desc><url>https://www.geocaching.com/seek/wpt.aspx?WID=17f70cb8-ae4a-4466-8b21-ff75b6d8d8dc</url><urlname>Parking</urlname><sym>Parking Area</sym><type>Waypoint|Parking Area</type></wpt><wpt lat="0" lon="0"><time>2007-05-20T19:45:07</time><name>0112E08</name><cmt /><desc>Series Final</desc><url>https://www.geocaching.com/seek/wpt.aspx?WID=cb4abfa2-8e74-4dbb-b733-f7db9a517e58</url><urlname>Series Final</urlname><sym>Final Location</sym><type>Waypoint|Final Location</type></wpt><wpt lat="44.27755" lon="-72.572017"><time>2006-08-07T05:59:56</time><name>PKXJHP</name><cmt>Parking for: Cache Across America - Vermont.</cmt><desc>Cache Across America VT Parking</desc><url>https://www.geocaching.com/seek/wpt.aspx?WID=d9e1979b-b64e-4015-adc7-94b10de627ac<