oad.</cmt><desc>Pumpelly Trailhead</desc><url>https://www.geocaching.com/seek/wpt.aspx?WID=84acac07-30fc-4a9f-be89-a8595a90a317</url><urlname>Pumpelly Trailhead</urlname><sym>Trailhead</sym><type>Waypoint|Trailhead</type></wpt><wpt lat="41.881117" lon="-71.521117"><time>2017-07-11T20:01:53</time><name>PK78QC5</name><cmt>At end of Carlton's Way Subdivision loop.  There is room for two vehicles only.  If these spaces are taken please proceed to the Mercer Outlook Parking area further up on Mountaindale Road.   Please DO NOT park on the Carlton's Trail ROADWAY.   Residents have complained that hikers (AND cachers!) have parked in front of their houses.   Please respect their wishes so that we won't have to move the cache.   THANK YOU.</cmt><desc>GC78QC5 Parking</desc><url>https://www.geocaching.com/seek/wpt.aspx?WID=abadc845-76f5-4a56-b8a6-dd1f94b0fc42</url><urlname>GC78QC5 Parking</urlname><sym>Parking Area</sym><type>Waypoint|Parking Area</type></wpt><wpt lat="39.804317" lon="-89.104333"><time>2019-04-12T08:24:09</time><name>0182Z45</name><cmt /><desc>Parking</desc><url>https://www.geocaching.com/seek/wpt.aspx?WID=6f5347eb-db38-4a48-904b-8bf0ebc418f3</url><urlname>Parking</urlname><sym>Parking Area</sym><type>Waypoint|Parking Area</type></wpt><wpt lat="42.669867" lon="-73.757667"><time>2019-10-10T16:27:04</time><name>018EHW7</name><cmt /><desc>Parking</desc><url>https://www.geocaching.com/seek/wpt.aspx?WID=b5907693-c20b-4526-b44b-040c28c2fcfd</url><urlname>Parking</urlname><sym>Parking Area</sym><type>Waypoint|Parking Area</type></wpt><wpt lat="42.469117" lon="-71.348267"><time>2021-04-01T08:02:15</time><name>0198G7V</name><cmt>Best location - Across from Minute Man Park - 5 minute walk to trail head</cmt><desc>Parking</desc><url>https://www.geocaching.com/seek/wpt.aspx?WID=c6f63ae3-5cf8-4b4d-a5be-5c678c49ec90</url><urlname>Parking</urlname><sym>Parking Area</sym><type>Waypoint|Parking Area</type></wpt><wpt lat="42.465967" lon="-71.347583"><time>2021-04-01T08:02:15</